FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Get answers to common queries about our sports app
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: What sports does your app cover?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app covers a wide range of sports including football, basketball, tennis, cricket, and many more. We're constantly expanding our coverage to include more sports and leagues.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: How do I track my favorite teams?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Simply search for your favorite teams in the app and tap the 'Follow' button. You'll then receive personalized updates, scores, and news about your chosen teams.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Is live streaming available on the app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Yes, we offer live streaming for select games and events. Check the 'Live' section of the app to see what's currently available for streaming.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: How often are scores and statistics updated?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: We update scores and statistics in real-time during live games. For completed games, final results are usually available within minutes of the game ending.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: Is there a cost to use the app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: The basic version of our app is free to use. We also offer a premium subscription with additional features such as ad-free experience, exclusive content, and advanced statistics.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: What sports does the app cover?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app covers a wide range of sports including football, basketball, tennis, golf, and many more. We're constantly expanding our coverage to include more sports and leagues.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: Is the app free to download?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Yes, the app is free to download. We offer a basic version with essential features at no cost, as well as premium options with advanced features for a small subscription fee.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: How often is the sports data updated?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Our app provides real-time updates for live games and events. Scores, statistics, and news are refreshed instantly to keep you up-to-date with all the latest sports action.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Can I personalize the app for my favorite teams?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Absolutely! You can customize your experience by selecting your favorite teams and sports. This allows you to receive tailored notifications, news, and highlights specific to your interests.
